$title
Timeline
$
The <b>Timeline</b> panel shows a chronological view of the items that are inside the Chart. The Timeline 
view has 5 tabs: Storyboard, Timing, Lanes; and if a lane is selected: Lane Steps (shown as Steps), 
and Hit Objects (shown as Hits). Below the Timeline are actions related to the Timeline and options 
to tweak the Timeline. 

