1. <indent=2em><b>Timeline Modes</b>
$n
List of the Timeline's available modes. Each mode changes the type of Objects that 
the Timeline shows.

$
2. <indent=2em><b>Timeline Body</b>
$n
The body of the Timeline panel, where the Timeline objects reside.

$
3. <indent=2em><b>Timeline Actions</b>
$n
The bottom left of the panel are Timeline Actions that contained basic actions 
that are used while editing such as: Undo, Redo, Cut, Copy, and Paste.

$
4. <indent=2em><b>Timeline Options</b>
$n
The bottom right of the panel are Timeline Options that contains basic timeline 
options such as the song's playback speed or the Timeline's separatoion factor.

$
5. <indent=2em><b>Extra Timeline Options Dropdown</b>
$n
Press the button to show and edit extra timeline options such as the waveform 
settings.